Package it.unipr.barbato.Interface.Message

package it.unipr.barbato.Interface.Message
The package it.unipr.barbato.Interface.Message contains classes and interfaces related to messaging in the distributed system. This package provides functionality for sending and receiving messages between different nodes in the distributed system.
